{"tid":774192,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳凱琳老母透bra 有無手足J到出血","createTime":"2018-08-10T06:43:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T15:31:01.000Z","uid":157545,"like":9,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6ed3950a31ff04570bc06f7728665d75eeabe02c","tid":774192,"uid":157545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T06:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180810/large/1533874505_f124.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180810%2Flarge%2F1533874505_f124.jpg&h=9d111b3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳凱琳（Grace）父母今早十時十五分現身機場，出發到峇里出席囡囡婚禮，陳父連聲感謝大家關心，並接受訪問，佢透露Grace同未來女婿鄭嘉穎噚日已經飛咗去峇里。捨得女兒嗎？陳父笑道：「嫁咗都會喺度㗎嘛！」<br />\n<br />\n印尼連日地震不斷，陳母坦言擔心，陳父就話：「婚禮係個女負責，唔關我事。」至於婚禮形式同賓客數目等問題，佢都係呢句：「全部係佢哋安排，唔到我哋話事，我係被動。」<br />\n咁，陳父有乜嘢係知道嘅呢？<br />\n佢就答：「我真係冇乜嘢知。」<br />\n<br />\n有傳Grace之後會喺加拿大補擺婚禮，呢樣陳父就知喇，答案係：No。<br />\n咁係咪會喺香港補擺酒？陳父又係呢句：「唔知道。」<br />\n<br />\n問到陳父畀未來女婿幾多分？他笑謂：「一定100分。唔係100分都唔畀個女嫁。」而向來都廿四孝嘅陳母同樣喜歡呢位未來女婿，表現風騷笑到四萬咁口，被問到今次係咪第一次放手？陳母話：「唔係，不嬲佢都有自己做。」仲叫大家「加油」！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180810/large/1533873665_4046.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180810%2Flarge%2F1533873665_4046.jpg&h=7778b3a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180810/large/1533873666_eb03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180810%2Flarge%2F1533873666_eb03.jpg&h=db6fd49f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180810/large/1533873669_8ab4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180810%2Flarge%2F1533873669_8ab4.jpg&h=f2634a63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180810/large/1533873666_eb03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180810%2Flarge%2F1533873666_eb03.jpg&h=db6fd49f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n膠穎食雞都要食親子井<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbceb220de7c36178aaf16b22ff2f981c6de0ca4","tid":774192,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T06:44:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92389803cf4b0b608e49398b98376967303d765b","tid":774192,"uid":33848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T06:44:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d972927a3bde0d69df198e1707ca62abf1cf47e","tid":774192,"uid":53672,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T06:44:43.000Z","msg":"佢老母咁狂野唔怪得。。。"},{"pid":"a17f70558970e327dfe432af9617e8f02dbc676d","tid":774192,"uid":31841,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T06:45:03.000Z","msg":"唔怪得俾印度人中出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db415074e5878035efcb7b049691d3840d122d78","tid":774192,"uid":17866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T06:45:11.000Z","msg":"好想同佢生mix. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e52e16761a486e57b8d5538576630f5133b6dd5","tid":774192,"uid":157545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a17f70558970e327dfe432af9617e8f02dbc676d","tid":774192,"uid":31841,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T06:45:03.000Z","msg":"唔怪